text: Rudolf "Rudi" Faßnacht (28 December 1934 in Neu-Ulm in Bavaria – 25 July 2000 in Gonesse) was a German football manager. Faßnacht coached MSV Duisburg. They finished 7th place in the 1970–71 Bundesliga. Faßnacht died along with his wife on board Air France Flight 4590, the Concorde which crashed in Gonesse, near Paris, on 25 July 2000. == Related pages == * Air France Flight 4590 == References == == Other websites == * * Category:1934 births Category:2000 deaths Category:German footballers Category:German football managers Category:MSV Duisburg managers Category:Arminia Bielefeld managers Category:Association football defenders Category:SC Preußen Münster managers Category:Tennis Borussia Berlin managers
